introducing taptica’s new vp product management tal dagan  blogtaptica loading sign up sign in english chinesejapanese menu back home tapticaaboutpresseventscase studiescareerscontact objectivesacquisitionmonetizationinsight mediumsmobilesocialvideodisplay innovationdmpdsp blog aboutpresseventscase studiescareerscontact us socialize with us introducing taptica’s new vp product management tal dagan january    article written by carly morris we’re starting off  with some exciting news about a big new addition to the taptica team as tal dagan joins our ranks as vp product management we’re thrilled to introduce our newest taptican an experienced leader with degrees in business administration computer science executive education and strategic marketing management as well as years of industry experience at haystackz flash networks comverse and emblaze with a passion for technology products and offroad bikes tal is ready to drive taptica’s game plan to the next level   “until now the market has been fragmented making it hard to develop coherent products however as things begin to consolidate more efficient tools can be developed resulting in higher conversion rates and lower costs for advertisers” says tal   but why the major shift presently the ad tech industry is a given as the world becomes increasingly mobilefirst and connected embracing programmatic is no longer a leap of faith but a reality this has pushed traditionally marketfocused organizations to fall flat as they squander their resources on further dissecting an already defined market the resulting move toward a stronger product focus is critical as the key issue facing the mobile ad tech industry is no longer about attracting new users to join the market but addressing the specific needs therein still this is not to say that taptica will be straying from our consumersided focus either while product is certainly a key focal point we still appreciate the importance of taking all sides into consideration for fullyinformed decision making and improvement a keen market focus will always be essential to stay on top of the latest mobile innovations as taptica continues to lead the ranks in product growth and development you can expect to see tal’s energized vision take center stage as he pioneers new initiatives to perfect the relationship between our product and our partners welcome aboard tal read more please choose an account to log into mobile click here social click here x close get access to a range of media sources delivering high quality and volume become an advertiser monetize your traffic and maximize your ecpm become a publisher x close fe investegate taptica int ltd announcements  taptica int ltd grant of options to pdmr we use cookies on our website if you continue to browse our website without taking any action we will assume that you are happy to receive all cookies from our website read more dismiss financial express holdings limited “we” “our” “us” and derivatives are committed to protecting and respecting your privacy this privacy policy together with our terms of use sets out the basis on which any personal data that we collect from you or that you provide to us will be processed by us relating to your use of any of the below websites “sites” feanalyticscom feinvestnet fetransmissioncom investegatecouk trustnethk trustnetoffshorecom trustnetmiddleeastcom for the purposes of the data protection act  the data controller is trustnet limited of nd floor golden house  great pulteney street london wf nn our nominated representative for the purpose of this act is kirsty witter what information do we collect about you we collect information about you when you register with us or use any of our websites  services part of the registration process may include entering personal details  details of your investments we may collect information about your computer including where available your operating system browser version domain name and ip address and details of the web