tion risks equities and currencies the firm rotates investments in asset allocation hedge design or the selection of alpha strategies aiming to add value and improve stability of return delivery details hidden slater investments ltd slater is a dedicated uk equity investor the large majority of the firms equity investments target midcap uk companies with marginal investments in smallcap and overseas stocks the funds may occasionally not be fully invested holding large amounts of cash or near cashto achieve capital growth the fund managers chase value stocks they target undervalued recovering companies following closely directors dealings and examining key quantitative data such as cash flow pricetosales ratio and pricetoresearch ratio they pick stocks without any particular reference to sector or index weightingsthe fund managers are personally invested in their fundsthe firm measure their funds performance against the fste all share details hidden herald investment management ltd himl is an active longterm manager which invests globally in listed and unlisted companies in the technology communications and media sectors they employ a bottomup approach to appraise potential investments fundamental financial analysis and traditional company research is supplemented both by company visits and regular meetings between himl and executive management teams details hidden herald investment management ltd himl is an active longterm manager which invests globally in listed and unlisted companies in the technology communications and media sectors they employ a bottomup approach to appraise potential investments fundamental financial analysis and traditional company research is supplemented both by company visits and regular meetings between himl and executive management teams details hidden river  mercantile asset management llp ramam is an active mediumterm manager which utilizes quantitative and fundamental analysis in their investment approach seeking absolute and relative 